@{
    
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
<style type="text/css">
   
    /* Style the tab content */
    .tabcontent {
        float: left;
        padding: 0px 12px;
        border: 0px solid #cadcf6;
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        color: #00408a !important;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    p {
        color: #3c586d;
        line-height: 30px;
    }

    li {
        color: #3c586d !important;
    }
</style>

<main id="content">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="bg-img-hero text-center mb-5 mb-lg-8" style="background-image: url('../Content/img/customer-care-service.jpg');">
        <div class="container space-top-xl-3 py-6 py-xl-0">
            <div class="row justify-content-center py-xl-4">
                <!-- Info -->
                <div class="py-xl-10 py-5">
                    <h1 class="font-size-40 font-size-xs-30 text-white font-weight-bold mb-0">Customer Care Service</h1>
                    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                        <ol class="breadcrumb breadcrumb-no-gutter justify-content-center mb-0">
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item font-size-14"><a class="text-white" href="@Data.GetMeRoom.GlobalConstant.ConfigVariables.SITEROOTPATH">Home</a></li>
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item custom-breadcrumb-item font-size-14 text-white active" aria-current="page">Customer Care Service</li>
                        </ol>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                <!-- End Info -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--End Hero Section -->
    <div class=" terms_tab border-bottom border-color-8 pt-lg-1">

        <div class="container mb-4 mb-lg-11 pb-lg-1">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                    <div id="about" class="tabcontent" style="padding: 25px; min-height: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important; display: block;">
                        <p>At BookMyHotels, we take pride in offering an impeccable range of tailor-made customer care services through our secure and user-friendly online platform. We value our guests and ensure that booking a hotel room is convenient, effortless, and available anytime, from anywhere.</p>

                        <p>Our dedicated ground support team is always reachable, quick to respond, and committed to providing prompt assistance. Whether you’re looking for affordable stays in India, budget hotels, or discounted accommodations across the world, you’ll find a wide selection right here on BookMyHotels.</p>


                        <h4 class="mt-4">We Help You from the Heart</h4>

                        <p>Finding the perfect accommodation can be challenging — and that’s exactly where BookMyHotels steps in. Our experienced support team works diligently to connect you with reliable budget hotels and luxury stays at attractive rates. We’re here to make your travel experience smoother and more enjoyable.</p>


                        <div class="mt-4 mb-4 p-3 border rounded">
                            <p><strong>📞 Call Us On:</strong> +91 11 4055 0926</p>
                            <p><strong>💬 Live Chat With Us:</strong> Available 08:00 AM – 09:00 PM (IST)</p>
                            <p><strong>🏨 Contact the Hotel:</strong> Direct contact details are shared in your booking confirmation.</p>
                        </div>



                        <h4 class="mt-5">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h4>

                       

                        <h5>Q1. How can I cancel my hotel booking?</h5>
                        <p>BookMyHotels allows guests to cancel their hotel bookings within 24 hours prior to check-in. Cancellation charges, if any, will be determined by the respective hotel based on their policies.</p>


                        <h5 class="mt-4">Q2. Is there a mandatory cancellation fee charged by the hotel?</h5>
                        <p>If your booking includes free cancellation, you will not be charged any fee. If your booking is non-refundable or partially refundable, the hotel may apply cancellation charges as per their policy. BookMyHotels does not determine or control hotel cancellation fees. Please refer to the respective hotel’s policy and our Terms &amp; Conditions for details on any applicable service fees.</p>


                        <h5 class="mt-4">Q3. Who charges my credit card when I make a hotel reservation, and when is the payment processed?</h5>
                        <p>In most cases, the hotel property will process the payment directly to your credit card. However, if BookMyHotels processes the payment, it will be clearly indicated in your booking confirmation.</p>

                        <p>Depending on the hotel’s payment policy, full pre-payment may be required, in which case the charge is processed at the time of booking. If a hotel requires a test payment to validate your card, the amount is temporarily held and refunded after you check in. Test payments are not actual charges but serve as a booking guarantee.</p>


                        <h5 class="mt-4">Q4. Can I make changes to my hotel booking?</h5>
                        <p>Yes. You can modify your booking through the confirmation email or directly via the BookMyHotels website, subject to the hotel’s policies. Possible changes include:</p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>Change check-in/check-out times</li>
                            <li>Modify dates</li>
                            <li>Cancel booking</li>
                            <li>Update payment details</li>
                            <li>Edit guest information</li>
                            <li>Select bed type</li>
                            <li>Change room category</li>
                            <li>Add a room or meal plan</li>
                            <li>Make a special request</li>
                            <li>Contact the property directly</li>
                        </ul>


                        <h5 class="mt-4">Q5. Can I book a hotel without a credit card?</h5>
                        <p>Generally, a valid credit or debit card is required to confirm a reservation. However, certain hotels listed on BookMyHotels allow bookings without pre-payment or card authorization. You may also use a third-party card (friend, spouse, or family member) provided you have their consent and include the cardholder’s name during booking.</p>


                        <hr class="mt-5">

                        <p>BookMyHotels strives to make your hotel booking experience smooth, transparent, and trustworthy. Whether it’s before, during, or after your stay — our team is here to assist you every step of the way.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

